ox}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2010-11 Cincinnati Bearcats men's basketball team}}\n[[Category:2010\u201311 Big East Conference men's basketball season|Cincinnati Bearcats]]\n[[Category:Cincinnati Bearcats men's basketball seasons]]\n[[Category:2011 NCAA Division I Men's Basketball Tournament participants|Cincinnati Bearcats]]\n[[Category:2010 in sports in Ohio|Cincin]]\n[[Category:2011 in sports in Ohio|Cincin]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|American college basketball season}}\n{{Infobox NCAA team season\n  |mode=Basketball\n  |year=2010-11\n  |prev_year=2009-10\n  |next_year=2011-12\n  |team=Cincinnati Bearcats\n  |image= Cincinnati University Bearcats textlogo.svg\n  |image_size=300px\n  |conference=Big East Conference (1979\u20132013)\n  |division=\n  |short_conf=Big East\n  |CoachRank=\n  |APRank=\n  |record=26&ndash;9\n  |conf_record=11&ndash;7\n  |head_coach=[[Mick Cronin (basketball coach)|Mick Cronin]]\n  |asst_coach1=\n  |asst_coach2=\n  |asst_coach3=\n  |stadium=[[Fifth Third Arena]]\n  |champion=\n  |bowl=NCAA Tournament\n  |bowl_result=Third Round\n}}\n{{2010&ndash;11 Big East men's basketball standings}}\nThe '''2010\u201311 Cincinnati Bearcats men's basketball team''' represents the [[University of Cincinnati]] during the [[2010\u201311 NCAA Division I men's basketball season]]. The team plays its home games in [[Cincinnati]] at the [[Fifth Third Arena]], which has a capacity of 13,176. They are members of the [[Big East Conference (1979\u20132013)|Big East Conference]].\n\n== Offseason ==\n\n=== Departing players ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"1\"\n! Name !! Number !! Pos. !! Height !! Weight !! Year !! Hometown !! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| {{sortname|Deonta|Vaughn}} || 5 || G || {{sort|74|6'1\"}} || 190 || {{sort|4|Senior}} || [[Indianapolis, Indiana]] || Graduated\n|-\n| {{sortname|Steve|Toyloy|nolink=1}} || 25 || C || {{sort|80|6'8\"}} || 255 || {{sort|4|Senior}} || [[West Palm Beach, Florida]] || Graduated\n|-\n| {{sortnam